ed throughput and latency shows that the system can feasibly compete\nwith solutions currently in use. Yet, further work is needed to demonstrate\nthese performance characteristics in an environment similar to that experienced\nin production.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2020 18:24:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Oct 2021 18:14:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-12"}
