ferent\nconditions, SMSs of masses $\\sim10^{3-5} \\,\\mathrm{M_{\\odot}}$ can form for all\nthree accretion scenarios considered in this work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2020 19:01:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 May 2021 18:00:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-18"}
