bular precursors. Presolar\nsilicates are unlikely to be present in high abundances in returned samples\nfrom asteroids Ryugu and Bennu since remote-sensing data indicate that they\nhave experienced substantial aqueous alteration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Dec 2020 15:42:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-28"}
